Figure 9. (left) G. tarkinense sp. nov., The Clump, north-west Tasmania, QVM 23:8056; SEM of gonopods in situ. Scale-bar = 0.5 mm. (right) G. tarkinense sp. nov., Wombat Hill, north-west Tasmania, QVM 23:8057; outline sketch of right gonopod showing course of prostatic groove (dashed line).
